{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"709a82d9cb","title":"对军委办公厅关于贯彻反官主义问题报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8929ad4816","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":23,"articleId":"709a82d9cb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"07b580b075","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指人民革命军事委员会办公厅主任肖向荣1952年10月21日关于贯彻反官像主义问题给彭德怀转毛泽东的报告。肖向荣在报告中说，处理文件上的拖延积压，主要原因是制度上存在若干缺点。“为了审查一件预算，从最初的编造机关起到最后的批准机关止，中间最少十几重层次，不知多少干部被压在没有必要的事务里，实在有加以改革之必要。最好是在军委设审计机关，凡经军委批准之工程，即可由原单位直接送审计机关审查，审计机关即有批准之权，不要层层审查，既拖延时间，又浪费人力。”"},{"id":"8d6f977578","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"f809923764","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d086a6066c","type":"title","text":"对军委办公厅关于贯彻反管概主义问题报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb"},{"id":"07b580b075","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请周一阅。关于军委设审计机关问题，似有必要；如同意，即请彭主办；如有意见，请与彭商处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb"},{"id":"8d6f977578","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb"},{"id":"f809923764","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb"}],"page":{"id":"6de984fb24","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"709a82d9cb","start":306,"end":306}}}},"__N_SSG":true}